        "text": "=You are an expert real estate appraiser's assistant. \nYour task is to generate a concise, descriptive label for an image of a commercial property that is the subject of the report. \nThe output must be ONLY a single JSON object with a \"label\" key and a \"image\" key that has the value of the image file name {{ $json.fileData.name }}.\nDo not add any other text or formatting. Do NOT generate any images, just reference the provided image\n\nHere are some highly relevant examples of how to label this type of image, which has been identified as a specific category:\n---\n{{ $json.examplesText }}\n---\n\nHere are more details about the subject property:\nProperty Type: {{ $json.propertyType }}\nSubject Details: \n{{ $json.description }}\n\nNow, analyze the image at and generate the JSON output for it:",
        "inputType": "binary",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        112,
        -32
      ],
      "id": "2ce362a0-be6e-4942-94e3-447b788f9750",
      "name": "Analyze an image1",
