        "text": "=You are an expert commercial real estate appraiser documenting a property inspection. This image has been labeled as: \"{{label}}\" and categorized as \"{{$json.category}}\" for a {{ $('When Executed by Another Workflow').item.json.propertyType }} property at .\n\nA short description of the subject property is as follows:\n{{ description }}\n\nDescribe what you observe in detail: materials, construction quality, approximate dimensions, condition, notable features, and any deficiencies or deferred maintenance. Be specific about material types (e.g., \"painted drywall\" not \"walls\", \"concrete slab\" not \"floor\"). This will be used as reference documentation for an appraisal report.\n\nRespond with only the description text, 2-4 sentences.\n\nWhen relevant to this image, note observations about the following building characteristics: foundation type, roof type and material, building frame, exterior wall material, floor material and finish, interior wall material and finish, ceiling type, lighting type, restroom fixtures, electrical systems, plumbing, HVAC systems, fire protection/sprinklers, elevators, site improvements (fencing, wells, septic, paving), landscaping, and parking surface type. Only mention characteristics that are actually visible in the image — do not speculate about what you cannot see.",
        "inputType": "binary",
        "binaryPropertyName": "={{ $('Edit Image').item.binary.data }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -608,
